body.name: Pre-Built Model Aircraft 1:200 for Peach Airlines Airbus A320neo Die-Casting Toy Airplanes for Fans Collect Souvenirs with Stand Airplane Model kit
features: 【Company Philosophy】Our passion is to capture the essence and cultural spirit of these classics, which are replica models of iconic classic micro-aircraft from different eras. Every detail is a testament to our passion for creativity and superior craftsmanship, ensuring each miniature model aircraft is a true work of art.

This miniature aircraft model is well-proportioned in size and heavy in the hand, showing a high degree of realism. The combination of aesthetic charm and detailed features makes people fascinated at first sight, creating an extremely realistic overall effect.

The outer shell of this aircraft model is made of high-strength alloy and processed by CNC to ensure accuracy and has good aging resistance and weldability. Other accessories (tires) are made of durable ABS engineering plastic and will not be easily deformed or damaged.

Rich in detail, the use of rubber stands to scale the aircraft model adds another layer of beauty to its display. Place the aviation model on the exhibition stand, allowing model enthusiasts to appreciate the exquisite details depicting the take-off state and flight of the aircraft.

【Service After Sales】In addition to a rich collection of classic aerospace models, we also offer a variety of automobile scale models. Whether you are an experienced collector or a fan who appreciates the miraculous beauty of these miniatures, we invite you to explore their mysteries together and we value your feedback and suggestions.
